{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01G7eaizkFq6yC3aU3Vt4Zuv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DHNY6e1BJzp7emMNMCnz41","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Read memory files and Top 3 Opportunities sheet","subagent_type":"Explore","prompt":"Read the following memory files and return their full contents:\n1. C:/Users/rjega/.claude/projects/C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis/memory/project_vendor_spend_analysis.md\n2. C:/Users/rjega/.claude/projects/C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis/memory/project_step06_rationale.md\n3. C:/Users/rjega/.claude/projects/C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis/memory/project_step07_consolidation.md\n4. C:/Users/rjega/.claude/projects/C--Users-rjega-vendor-spend-analysis/memory/project_step08_strategic_scores.md\n\nThen, run this Python script to extract the \"Top 3 Opportunities\" sheet from the workbook:\n\n```python\nimport openpyxl\nwb = openpyxl.load_workbook(\"C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx\")\nprint(\"Sheets:\", wb.sheetnames)\nws = wb[\"Top 3 Opportunities\"]\nfor row in ws.iter_rows(values_only=True):\n    print(row)\n```\n\nReturn all file contents and the script output."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1916,"cache_read_input_tokens":14418,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1916,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"287e74d1-c222-46fc-97c3-6b14ad8ff5d8","uuid":"676b5596-330b-4b9a-86f6-e34578252c9d"}
